# Skills, manifests, and queries are synced into this agent's root from the
# repository-root .github/ and queries/ by deploy.sh (sync_github_assets). The
# root repo is the single source of truth; these copies exist only so the
# Dockerfile can bundle them into the hosted-agent image (COPY . user_agent/).
# Never commit them here — they would duplicate the root tree and drift.
skills/
manifests/
queries/
